title.rendered: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness

content.rendered:
Doctor Strange, aided by mystical allies old and new, travels through the mind-bending and dangerous alternate realities of the Multiverse to confront a mysterious new adversary.

Directed By Sam Raimi

Written By Michael Waldron. Stan Lee. Steve Ditko

Stars: Benedict Cumberbatch. Elizabeth Olsen. Chiwetel Ejiofor
